iBART v0.0.2.2 (Release date: 2022-03-07)
==============

Changes:

* If iBART didn't select any features in 2 consecutive iterations, it will report
  the latest good results.


iBART v0.0.2.1 (Release date: 2021-10-28)
==============

Changes:

* Remove changes from iBART v0.0.2.0
* Add options to select variable selection criterion used by bartMachine. Three
  options are available: "global_se", "global_max", and "local". The default
  criterion is "global_se". See var_selection_by_permute in R package bartMachine
  for more detail.


iBART v0.0.2.0 (Release date: 2021-08-31)
==============

Changes:

* Added progress bar function for R shiny application.
* Added Lzero_descriptor to output the values of the selected descriptors.


iBART v0.0.1.9 (Release date: 2021-08-05)
==============

Changes:

* Added warnings for applying binary operators with less than 2 columns and for
  applying unary operators with no columns.


iBART v0.0.1.8 (Release date: 2021-07-14)
==============

Changes:

* Corrected issue when BART-G.SE only selects one variable


iBART v0.0.1.7 (Release date: 2021-07-05)
==============

Changes:

* Corrected standardize for lm


iBART v0.0.1.6 (Release date: 2021-06-25)
==============

Changes:

* Tested for R 4.1.0 and glmnet v4.1-2


iBART v0.0.1.5 (Release date: 2021-06-23)
==============

Changes:

* Bugs fixed.

